OL,3,CThief caught snatching phone in Soho
OL,4,Ccaught by two undercover police
OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,FA brazen thief was caught by two
OL,8,Fundercover police officers after
OL,9,Fsnatching a phone in the heart of Soho.
OL,11,FCCTV caught the moment a man dressed
OL,12,Fin white ran across the road and stole
OL,13,Fa mobile phone from the back pocket of
OL,14,Fhis victim.
OL,16,FThe two officers jumped into action
OL,17,Fand tackled the thief before returning
OL,18,Fit to its unwitting owner.
