OL,7,FKadi Nasser, 25, was charged with
OL,8,Ftheft before he was remanded in
OL,9,Fcustody. He appeared at Westminster
OL,10,FMagistrates Court on Monday, 8 July
OL,11,Fwhere he pleaded guilty to theft and
OL,12,Fwas jailed for 30 weeks.
