OL,7,FDetective Superintendent Saj Hussain,
OL,8,Fwho leads on phone robbery and theft
OL,9,Fin the Met, said: "Robbery and theft
OL,10,Fare invasive and often violent crimes.
OL,11,FI want to therefore applaud the quick-
OL,12,Fthinking actions of these two officers
OL,13,Ffor returning the victim's phone,
OL,14,Fputting a street thief behind bars,
OL,15,Fand helping to make London safer.
