OL,7,F"Met officers are targeting resources
OL,8,Fto hotspot areas, such as Westminster
OL,9,Fand Croydon, with increased patrols
OL,10,Fand plain clothes officers. These
OL,11,Fdeter criminals and make officers more
OL,12,Fvisibly available to members of the
OL,13,Fcommunity.
OL,15,F"We encourage people to report as soon
OL,16,Fas they can whenever they have been a
OL,17,Fvictim of robbery or theft, so
OL,18,Fofficers can attend the scene and
OL,19,Finvestigate swiftly."
